data.description: This new-construction home at Old Gilliam Crossing was designed to exceed your expectations with its massive space and the detailed features. Residents can look forward to hosting in the home’s formal dining and living room, family room and chef-ready kitchen. In the heart of the home, granite countertops encompass a full suite of energy-efficient appliances and beautiful upper-wood cabinets. A total of four bedrooms are located on the second floor, including the secluded master bedroom. This room features a full bath with a separate shower and soaker tub and two sizable walk-in closets! Residents can enjoy an array of amenities including a children’s playground, walking trails and a picnic pavilion in the neighborhood.
